# Backend Skill Roadmap (9 LPA → 30–40 LPA)

## Goal

Become **product-level backend engineer** (Laravel → Scalable Systems)

---

## 1. Core Backend (Must Master)

* System Design (HLD + LLD)
* REST API Design (scalable)
* Database Optimization (index, joins, partitioning)
* Transactions (DB consistency)
* Query Optimization (EXPLAIN, indexing)

---

## 2. Laravel Advanced

* Service Layer Architecture
* Jobs & Queues
* Events & Observers
* Caching (Redis)
* Error Handling & Logging

---

## 3. Scalability (Product Level)

* Redis (cache + session)
* Queue (async processing)
* Load Balancer (Nginx / AWS ELB)
* Microservices architecture
* Kafka (event-driven systems)
* Rate limiting & throttling

---

## 4. DSA (For Interviews)

* Arrays & Hashing
* Sliding Window
* Two Pointers
* Recursion basics

---

## 5. Real Projects (Important)

Build at least 2:

1. QR Code Tracking System

   * Scan → Track → Dashboard

2. Scalable API System

   * Redis + Queue + Cache

---

## 6. Testing & Quality

* Unit Testing (PHPUnit)
* API Testing
* Edge case handling

---

## 7. Timeline

0–3 Months

* Laravel deep + DSA

3–6 Months

* System Design + Redis + Queue

6–9 Months

* Kafka + Microservices

---

## Final Focus

* Clean code
* Performance
* Scalability
* Real projects
* Interview preparation

---

## Result

→ Product company ready
→ Target: 30–40 LPA 🚀
